entries.arrival_phase_1: Stand by.  We will send you information regarding the flight path of the enemy vessel.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Target locked.  Intercept the mining vessel, destroy it, and make sure there are no witnesses left alive to tell the tale.
entries.assassinate_success: That cargo will not make it out of the zone thanks to you.  Return to base and report to Captain Koh.
entries.destroy_escort: Eliminate the escort fighters.  There must be no witnesses.
entries.escort_remaining: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <%DI escort fighters remaining.>
entries.failed_escape: Well THAT didn't go very well.  So much for stopping that cargo.  You can explain your failure later to Captain Koh.
entries.quest_escort_d: Destroy all the escort ships guarding the mining vessel.
entries.quest_target_d: Once you have intercepted the ship, destroy it and all the escort fighters that guard it.
entries.quest_target_t: Intercept and Destroy The Gilded Wookiee
entries.title: Kashyyyk System:  Intercept the Gilded Wookiee
entries.title_d: Intercept the mining vessel 'The Gilded Wookiee' as it tries to use the path you cleared previously for the mining convoy to leave the zone.
